{%- comment -%}
  LIFETIME — Quiz v2 Loading-Screen

  3-Sekunden-Übergang nach Q7. CSS-Animationen laufen ab dem Moment,
  in dem der Step `.is-active` wird. JS triggert automatischen
  Übergang zur Result-Page nach 3000ms (LOADING_DURATION_MS).

  Aufbau:
    - Kreisförmiger Progress (SVG, stroke-dashoffset von 283 → 0)
    - Headline "Wir analysieren deine Antworten…"
    - 3 rotierende Sub-Texte (1s je, opacity-Animation gestaffelt)
    - Trust-Badge unten (Limmroth)
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="lt-quiz-loading" data-quiz-loading>
  <div class="lt-quiz-loading__center">
    <div class="lt-quiz-loading__progress" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="lt-quiz-loading__svg" focusable="false">
        <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="45" class="lt-quiz-loading__track"></circle>
        <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="45" class="lt-quiz-loading__bar"></circle>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <h2 class="lt-quiz-loading__title">Wir analysieren deine Antworten…</h2>

    <ul class="lt-quiz-loading__steps" aria-live="polite">
      <li class="lt-quiz-loading__step">
        <span class="lt-quiz-loading__step-icon" aria-hidden="true"><i class="ph-thin ph-check"></i></span>
        <span class="lt-quiz-loading__step-text">Deine 7 Antworten erfasst</span>
      </li>
      <li class="lt-quiz-loading__step">
        <span class="lt-quiz-loading__step-icon" aria-hidden="true"><i class="ph-thin ph-check"></i></span>
        <span class="lt-quiz-loading__step-text">Abgleich mit 22 DNA-Bereichen</span>
      </li>
      <li class="lt-quiz-loading__step">
        <span class="lt-quiz-loading__step-icon" aria-hidden="true"><i class="ph-thin ph-check"></i></span>
        <span class="lt-quiz-loading__step-text">Top-3-Themen identifiziert</span>
      </li>
      <li class="lt-quiz-loading__step">
        <span class="lt-quiz-loading__step-icon" aria-hidden="true"><i class="ph-thin ph-check"></i></span>
        <span class="lt-quiz-loading__step-text">Relevante Gene zugeordnet</span>
      </li>
      <li class="lt-quiz-loading__step">
        <span class="lt-quiz-loading__step-icon" aria-hidden="true"><i class="ph-thin ph-check"></i></span>
        <span class="lt-quiz-loading__step-text">Ergebnis vorbereitet</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p class="lt-quiz-loading__trust">
    Wissenschaftlich begleitet von Prof. Dr. med. Volker Limmroth
  </p>
</div>
